title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Must have gadget for travellers
body:
I purchased the Boldfit luggage weighing scale before my trip to Europe and I am very glad I did. It is a very handy and accurate device that saved me from paying extra fees at the airports. It is very easy to use, just hook your luggage to the strap and lift it up. The LCD display shows the weight in kilograms or pounds, I could carry it in my hand luggage without any problem. It has a long battery life and an auto shut-off feature to conserve power. It is also very durable and sturdy, and can weigh up to 50 kg. I highly recommend this product to anyone who travels frequently and wants to avoid excess luggage charges.

product: Wesley Milestone 2.0 Casual Waterproof Laptop Backpack/Office Bag/School Bag/College Bag/Business Bag/Travel Backpack (Dim...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Versatile and Reliable Companion for All Your Needs
body:
I recently purchased the Wesley Milestone 2.0 Casual Waterproof Laptop Backpack, and it has exceeded my expectations in terms of functionality, durability, and style. This backpack has quickly become my go-to companion for various occasions, whether it's for work, school, travel, or everyday use.One of the standout features of this backpack is its impressive storage capacity. With dimensions of 13x18 inches and a spacious 30L capacity, it easily accommodates my 15.6-inch laptop, books, notebooks, and other essentials without feeling bulky or overwhelming. The well-designed compartments and pockets help me keep my belongings organized and easily accessible. The laptop compartment is well-padded, providing excellent protection for my device.The waterproof feature of the backpack is a significant advantage, especially during unexpected weather conditions or accidental spills. It gives me peace of mind, knowing that my belongings are safe and protected from moisture.The build quality of the Wesley Milestone 2.0 backpack is outstanding. The materials used are durable and show no signs of wear even after months of daily use. The zippers are sturdy and glide smoothly, ensuring easy access to my belongings. The reinforced stitching adds to the overall durability and longevity of the backpack.Comfort is another aspect where this backpack shines. The ergonomic design, padded shoulder straps, and back panel provide excellent support and distribute the weight evenly, even when carrying heavy loads. The adjustable straps allow for a customized fit, reducing strain and fatigue during extended periods of wear.The stylish design of the backpack is an added bonus. The blue and black color combination is visually appealing and versatile, suitable for both casual and professional settings. The sleek and minimalistic look adds a touch of sophistication while maintaining a practical and functional design.Whether I'm commuting to the office, attending classes, or embarking on a weekend getaway, the Wesley Milestone 2.0 Casual Waterproof Laptop Backpack has proven to be a reliable and versatile companion. Its durability, ample storage, comfort, and stylish design make it a standout choice in the market.In conclusion, I highly recommend the Wesley Milestone 2.0 Casual Waterproof Laptop Backpack to anyone in need of a dependable and multi-functional bag. Its quality craftsmanship, spaciousness, and attractive design make it a worthwhile investment that will serve you well in various situations for years to come.

product: Wesley Unisex Milestone Casual Waterproof Laptop Office School College Business Travel Backpack 25 L (Dimensions: 12.5x18 ...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Perfect Blend of Style, Durability, and Functionality!
body:
I recently purchased the Wesley Unisex Milestone Casual Waterproof Laptop Office School College Business Travel Backpack, and it has quickly become my go-to bag for all occasions. This backpack seamlessly combines style, durability, and functionality, making it an excellent choice for anyone in need of a versatile and reliable bag.Firstly, the design is sleek and modern, making it suitable for both professional and casual settings. The unisex style means it can be comfortably used by anyone, and it doesn't look out of place whether I'm heading to the office, school, or a weekend getaway.The dimensions (12.5x18 inches) are perfect for carrying all my essentials without being overly bulky. It's spacious enough to fit my 15.6-inch laptop securely, along with books, a water bottle, and various other items. The compartments are thoughtfully designed, providing ample storage and easy organization for all my belongings.One of the standout features is its waterproof capability. Living in a city where unexpected rain showers are common, this backpack has been a lifesaver. I no longer worry about my electronics or important documents getting wet. The quality of the material is top-notch, and it feels sturdy enough to withstand daily wear and tear.Comfort is another big plus. The padded straps are adjustable and provide excellent support, even when the bag is fully loaded. I can carry it for hours without any discomfort, which is a huge advantage for someone who is constantly on the move.Overall, the Wesley Unisex Milestone Casual Waterproof Laptop Backpack has exceeded my expectations. It's a stylish, durable, and highly functional backpack that caters to all my needs. I highly recommend it to anyone looking for a reliable and versatile backpack for everyday use.

body:
Overall: 3 stars - This toilet cleaner gets the job done but has a few drawbacks.Pros:Effective Cleaning: Removes light stains and grime reasonably well.Germ Killing: Kills 99.9% of germs according to the label, which is a plus for hygiene.Value Pack: The double pack is economical, especially if you clean your toilets frequently.Easy to Use: The bottle has a convenient nozzle for reaching under the rim and into corners.Cons:Limited Stain Removal: Struggles with tougher stains or heavy buildup. May require scrubbing for stubborn marks.Light Scent: The rose fragrance is pleasant but fades quickly. Some users might prefer a stronger scent for lingering freshness.Unknown Strength: The lack of specific information about the disinfecting ingredients makes it difficult to gauge its effectiveness against certain bacteria or viruses.Recommendation:This is an okay toilet cleaner for basic cleaning and germ reduction. It's a good option for those on a budget who don't mind a lighter fragrance. However, if you're dealing with tough stains or require a powerful disinfectant with a long-lasting scent, you might want to consider a different product.Additional Notes:Always wear gloves when using any toilet cleaner.Ensure proper ventilation while using the product.For tough stains, consider using a stronger cleaner or a toilet bowl ring to prevent future buildup.I hope this review helps!

Sits very lightly on your face and even with makeup, this doesn't feel heavy. No breakouts, no pigmentation, no excess sebum production (which lead to white heads). Every time we have to press the button to go to the main page.  • Customise page option is not there.  Favorites:  • Design, lightweight, LCD display brightness, The Watch colour is also impressive & stylish to wear  •  AI assistance works perfectly.  • One of the best is smart mode on/off option which is very useful.  • Screen wake up sensors are working properly, which is preferable to use.

product: Fastrack New Reflex VOX 2.0 Black Smart Watch|BT Calling|1.8" HD Display|TWS Connect|AI Voice|50+ Sports Modes|100+ Watchf...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Needs improvement
body:
I have used this watch for a week.Things i liked:As an average gym goer, I find it pretty useful. It has no gps. Not totally accurate also. But I wanted a watch which had inbuilt music storage and to remind me to move all day and to drink water which it does very well. I also liked the fastrack reflex world app and the watch display features. Regarding connectivity with the app, if it does not connect immediately, just switching off the Bluetooth and switching it on will solve the issue. I will update battery life after using music features daily. So far with occasional music play.. 3hrs in a week, it lasted for a weekThings I didn't like:It says the watch display will be on when we lift to view it- good concept but it does not work. Also we have to change the multisport activity, it will not detect automatically.Pros.Inbuilt music storageGood speakerSedentary alert- to keep moving all dayHydration alertCons.Not accurateNo gpsDisplay.. lift to viewUpdate: After using for around 7hrs a day of music and for Bluetooth calling, battery lasted for around 3 days. But the charging is fast. It comes with a magnet battery and in 15 min it gets charged by 40 % , so I charge it when I go to take a shower, so it's not a problem for me.Regarding water proof,it has IP68 I've not immersed it in water as in swimming , but have poured water while washing hands and its working well. They have given a water draining option also.It would have been better if they gave an option for editing the shortcuts as I use music often than for calls, so I would have kept music as the second shortcut instead of AI

It's flexible enough to provide a comfortable fit without sacrificing durability. The sizing was accurate, and the belt sits comfortably on the waist without being too tight or too loose.Durability:After using the Labnoft belt for a few weeks, I can confidently say that it's built to last. The leather seems resistant to scratches and wear, and the buckle hasn't shown any signs of tarnish. This is the kind of belt that will be a staple in my wardrobe for years to come.Value for Money:Considering the quality and design, the Labnoft leather belt offers great value for money. It's a stylish accessory that doesn't break the bank, making it a smart investment for anyone in need of a reliable and fashionable belt.Conclusion:In conclusion, I highly recommend the Labnoft leather belt for those in search of a high-quality, stylish accessory. body:
So here is the thing, I purchased these along with another pair for me & my friend. The fit is nice and is also comfortable to wear. They don't slip, break or make you uncomfortable.The problem is with the kind of material used to make these slippers & it is a huge problem. So when you start to wear them you will not notice it, but after a week of usage, you will have stinky feet because no matter how hard you try to wash these slippers they will always feel sticky. No amount of rubbing with soap of any quality is going to help, it absorbs your sweat & doesn't let go making it a really dirty feeling.You will feel that it's maybe because of your socks, your shoes, or maybe you just did use the shoes for a longer period but the real culprit are the slippers, which you must have been using for 5-6 hours on daily basis.Only after changing the slippers to a different brand, I was able to find the difference.SO BEWARE!

"Durable and Long-lasting!": I've had my Crocs Literide for months now, and they still look and feel as good as the day I bought them. Whether I'm walking through puddles, navigating rocky terrain, or just lounging around the house, these shoes never disappoint. They're truly a testament to Crocs' commitment to quality and innovation.5. "The Ultimate Travel Companion!": If you're a frequent traveler like me, the Crocs Literide is an absolute must-have. title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Casio
body:
The Casio AE-1200, also known as the Casio World Time, boasts a range of features that make it a standout choice in its price range.1. **World Time Functionality:** One of its key features is the ability to display time in multiple cities worldwide, making it an excellent companion for travelers or those dealing with international contacts.2. **Durable Build:** The watch is known for its robust construction. The rugged design ensures it can withstand daily wear and tear, making it a reliable option for various activities.3. **Multiple Alarms:** With multiple alarms, the AE-1200 offers versatility for setting reminders throughout the day. This is particularly useful for those with busy schedules.4. **LED Backlight:** The inclusion of an LED backlight enhances visibility in low-light conditions, providing practicality and ensuring you can read the time regardless of the environment.5. **Affordability:** One of its major advantages is its affordability. For a relatively low price, users get a watch with a range of features that are usually found in more expensive models.6. **Battery Life:** The watch typically has a long battery life, reducing the need for frequent replacements and ensuring it remains functional for an extended period.In summary, the Casio AE-1200 is a feature-packed watch that offers excellent value for money. Its combination of world time functionality, durability, multiple alarms, LED backlight, and affordability make it a practical and reliable choice for a wide range of users.

product: Casio Youth-Digital Grey Dial Men's Watch-AE-1200WH-1AVDF (D097)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Cool watch!
body:
This is my first ever Casio watch! I loved its design!There are many reviews and videos about the watch so i wont cover the obvious features but some of the lesser known points worth noting:1. The back-light is from two leds at the bottom corners. It is sufficient to view in complete darkness. The time for which the leds stay on upon pressing the button is configurable up to 3 seconds.2. The buttons when pressed create a sound but it can be disabled by holding the 'mode' button for few seconds. The display shows "mute" when the sound is disabled. Alarm sound is active even if "Mute" mode is selected.3. The clock is capable of giving hourly chime. When activated the display shows "SIG". It can be disabled in the settings.4. The belt if broken can be replaced by original or third party belts.5. Here is a small hint. In order to get perfect time for various time zones you need to check online if the DST is going on in that particular region or not. DST has to be selected as ON to match the current time in that city/timezone.6. It has 5 Alarms that can be set. You can set its occurrence for 'one time only ' or 'daily' . The alarm sound is enough to wake you up. It keeps going on for certain time but you can interrupt it to stop by pressing any button. "ALM" is displayed on upper right screen when alarm is set.7. The digitized analog clock (Round clock on upper left side) always shows the home city time (T1)8. There is a timer and stop watch function which works well.8. Please register the watch online at the given website link in the box.9. 10 years battery life is claimed, lets see how much it gives realistically.My favorite features which i find most useful:1. World time. I have set it as follows 1) T1= DEL (Delhi)as Current home time 2) T2= LON (London) time 3) T3=BER (Berlin) time 4) T4= LAX (Los Angles) time. The T2, T3, T4 are currently with DST set as ON.2. 5 Alarms: To wake up, For my child's school bus, For my Bus.3. Hourly Chime: Very handy to have a sense of time without looking.4. I have not found an occasion to use timer, stop watch etc yet but should be useful for some one into sports or cooking.Worth the price! Loved it!

product: Park Avenue Signature Collection Premium Body Spray for Men, 2 Voyage & 1 Neo FREE, Fresh Long Lasting Fragrance (Pack of ...
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Elevate Your Scent Game: Park Avenue Voyage & Neo Signature Collection Review
body:
The Park Avenue Voyage & Neo Signature Collection is a sophisticated and versatile fragrance set that adds a touch of elegance to any grooming routine. As someone who appreciates fine fragrances, I've been thoroughly impressed by the quality and distinctiveness of these scents.Let's start with the Voyage collection. The fragrances in this set evoke a sense of adventure and exploration, with notes that transport you to far-off destinations. Whether you're navigating the bustling streets of a cosmopolitan city or basking in the serenity of a tropical paradise, each scent in the Voyage collection captures a unique essence that is both captivating and invigorating.On the other hand, the Neo Signature collection offers a more refined and modern take on classic scents. With sophisticated notes that exude confidence and sophistication, these fragrances are perfect for making a statement in any setting. Whether you're heading to a business meeting or a social event, the Neo Signature collection ensures that you leave a lasting impression wherever you go.One aspect I particularly appreciate about both collections is their longevity and sillage. The fragrances last throughout the day, providing a subtle yet noticeable scent that lingers without being overpowering. Plus, the sleek and stylish packaging adds a touch of luxury to your grooming routine, making these fragrances a welcome addition to any bathroom or vanity.Another highlight of the Voyage & Neo Signature Collection is its versatility. Whether you prefer a light and refreshing scent for daytime wear or a rich and aromatic fragrance for evenings, there's something for every occasion in this set. Plus, the compact size of the bottles makes them perfect for travel, allowing you to take your favorite scents with you wherever you go.Overall, the Park Avenue Voyage & Neo Signature Collection is a must-have for anyone who appreciates fine fragrances. With its diverse range of scents, long-lasting performance, and elegant packaging, it's the perfect choice for elevating your scent game and making a lasting impression wherever you go.

product: Supersox Men's Half Terry Cotton Cushion Special Design Sneaker Length Socks (Multicolor, Free Size) Pack of 3
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Comfortable and Durable Cotton Socks
body:
I recently purchased a pair of cotton socks from Supersox and I've been thoroughly impressed with their performance. Here's my detailed review:Comfort: These socks are incredibly comfortable to wear. The cotton fabric is soft and gentle on the skin, providing a cozy feel throughout the day. I appreciate how breathable they are, keeping my feet cool and dry even during long hours of wear.Fit: The fit of these socks is spot on. They hug my feet snugly without feeling too tight, and the elasticated cuffs ensure they stay in place without slipping down or bunching up inside my shoes. It's evident that attention has been paid to getting the fit just right.Durability: I've been wearing these socks regularly for several weeks now, and I'm pleased to report that they've held up exceptionally well. Despite numerous washes, they show no signs of wear and tear, with the fabric retaining its shape and integrity. The reinforced heel and toe areas provide added durability, ensuring these socks will last for the long haul.Design: The design of these socks is simple yet effective. I appreciate the understated aesthetic, and the subtle branding adds a nice touch without being too flashy. The seamless construction means there are no uncomfortable seams to irritate my feet, enhancing the overall comfort level.Price: While these socks may be priced slightly higher than some other options on the market, I believe they offer excellent value for money. The quality of the materials and construction justifies the price, and considering their durability, they're a worthwhile investment in the long run.Overall Impression: In conclusion, I couldn't be happier with my purchase of these cotton socks from Supersox. They tick all the boxes in terms of comfort, fit, durability, and design. If you're in the market for high-quality socks that won't disappoint, I highly recommend giving these a try.Pros:Exceptional comfortPerfect fitOutstanding durabilitySleek designGood value for moneyCons:nothing

The liquid formula dissolves quickly in water, ensuring even distribution and thorough cleaning in every wash cycle. The fragrance is pleasant and leaves clothes smelling fresh. The mega saver pack provides great value for money, lasting for an extended period, which is perfect for households with frequent laundry needs. product: QUXIS Resistance Exercise Bands with Door Anchor, Handles, Waterproof Carry Bag, Legs Ankle Straps for Resistance Trainin...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Decent for the price pro/con
body:
If you're a beginner or an intermediate at resistance training, this is a good start for you.PROS:- Overall quality is above average.- The actual bands feel 'safe' and can be stretched to about 2.0 x the original length. (I'm 5'11" and they're fine in case that helps)- The door anchor is actually very good. Make sure you check that you have gotten it hooked it really.- The handles are comfortable and strong at full extension- The change in resistance is quite smooth as you pull. I have come across sets where the resistance is not gradual.- Quite quiet!- A chart for beginner's exercises is provided (yes, in English). I would suggest you find more extensive and detailed exercises online though.- The bag provided is more valuable than you would think. Really helps with keeping it all together and portability if you happen to go out of station for a while.- There are a lot, and I mean a lot, of exercises you can use them for. I watched a YT video where the trainer showed over 60 exercises! This is true for most resistance bands thoughCONS:- The ankle bands are a little thin, and the velcro will probably last a couple of months before losing grip, but a lot of the exercises can be done without them.- The metal hooks are where my issue was. They do not feel too safe, although they haven't broken for many months (according to a friend who has been using them daily for the past 4 months)BOTTOM LINE:They are as good as what you're paying for them, maybe a little better. If you're starting out and want to see if resistance training is for you, they're perfect. If you're using them in tandem with actual weight training, they're great.You will not repent spending the money if you fall under the above categories.SUGGESTIONS:- If you're using them for intense training, I would pay a little more and get a better set.- Make sure you purchase full-hand workout gloves! All resistance bands are tough on the skin, especially if the material used is not made of finely combed wrapping.Get fit!

As a professional international public figure constantly on the move, I have come to rely on this remarkable personal fan to keep me cool, composed, and ready to take on the challenges of my demanding lifestyle. In this comprehensive review, I will highlight the reasons why the Bajaj Pygmy Mini has become an essential companion for professionals seeking superior performance, elegant design, and portability.Efficient Performance:One of the standout features of the Bajaj Pygmy Mini is its exceptional performance. Despite its compact size, this fan delivers an impressive airflow that provides instant relief from the sweltering heat. Whether I'm in my office, attending meetings, or traveling, the Pygmy Mini's powerful airflow ensures that I remain cool and comfortable, enhancing my focus and productivity. The three-speed settings allow me to tailor the fan's performance according to my preferences, making it adaptable to different environments and weather conditions.Sleek and Stylish Design:As a professional international public figure, maintaining an elegant and sophisticated image is crucial. The Bajaj Pygmy Mini excels not only in performance but also in design. Its sleek and stylish appearance effortlessly complements any professional setting, blending seamlessly with both contemporary and traditional decor. The choice of colors, combined with its compact size, makes it an aesthetically pleasing addition to any workspace or room.Quiet Operation:In my line of work, silence is often golden. Whether I'm giving interviews, participating in video conferences, or simply seeking a peaceful environment, the Bajaj Pygmy Mini's whisper-quiet operation is a true blessing. This fan ensures that I can enjoy its cooling benefits without any disruptive noise, maintaining the tranquility necessary for effective communication and concentration.Portability at its Best:The life of a professional international public figure involves constant travel and shifting locations. The Pygmy Mini's compact size and lightweight design make it an ideal travel companion. It easily fits into my luggage, and its foldable stand ensures that I can position it conveniently in hotel rooms, temporary offices, or even during outdoor events. This portability factor is a significant advantage, allowing me to carry comfort and relief wherever I go.Durability and Longevity:Investing in quality products is a must for professionals, and the Bajaj Pygmy Mini certainly lives up to that expectation. Built with high-grade materials, this personal fan exhibits remarkable durability and longevity. It can withstand the rigors of frequent use, making it a reliable asset for professionals who require consistent performance over time. This level of durability is essential for maintaining a seamless routine, even in the face of hectic schedules.Energy Efficiency:In an era where sustainability is a top concern, the Bajaj Pygmy Mini shines as an energy-efficient appliance. Its low power consumption ensures that I can enjoy its benefits without worrying about inflated energy bills. This aligns perfectly with my commitment to minimizing my carbon footprint while still enjoying modern comforts. The Pygmy Mini serves as an example of how technology can enhance our lives without compromising our environmental responsibilities.Easy Maintenance:The demands of my profession leave me with limited time for intricate maintenance routines. The Pygmy Mini's user-friendly design simplifies maintenance tasks. Its detachable front grill makes it easy to clean, ensuring that the fan continues to operate at optimal performance levels. This convenient feature saves time and effort, allowing me to focus on my work and engagements without worrying about cumbersome maintenance requirements.Conclusion:As a professional international public figure, my endorsement of the Bajaj Pygmy Mini 110 mm Personal Fan is a testament to its remarkable qualities and outstanding performance. In a world where comfort, style, and efficiency are paramount, this fan excels on all fronts. Its efficient performance, sleek design, portability, and durability make it a must-have accessory for professionals who are constantly on the move. The Pygmy Mini's quiet operation, energy efficiency, and easy maintenance further cement its status as a superior personal fan that caters to the needs of modern professionals. With the Bajaj Pygmy Mini by your side, you can confidently face any situation, knowing that you have a reliable and elegant solution to beat the heat and maintain your professional composure.

product: Bajaj PYGMY MINI 110 MM PERSONAL FAN - WHITE SMOKE, small
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Good Product
body:
Functionalities of the fan is as mentioned in the description of it. There is no noticeable difference or downgrade in the actual item.The fan is lightweight thus really portable (that is the point if being small though).The fan has three speed modes and two LED light modes. Which speed mode is in use is indicated by different indicating light colors (green-slowest, blue-medium, greenish blue-fastest).Considering the fan is fullly charged --On slowest speed it runs for ~4 hrOn medium speed it runs for ~3 hrOn highest speed it runs for ~2 hrsKeeping the LED lights on (even in the high setting) wouldn't make much difference in the fan’s total runtime for each speed settingI am saying these from my testing of the speed modes which is no less than what the brand claims, even better sometimes.Speed of the fan is not really that much high (even in max speed). But at max speed it should be enough to get you through a few hours of power cut or similar situation.Main cage body containing the fan blades is upside down rotatable within the outer support ring.On charging, ‘full charged’ status is indicated by green light and ‘still charging’ is indicated by red light.Overall a quite good product.

product: Medimix Ayurvedic Classic 18 Herbs Soap, 125 g (Pack of 8)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Best soap. No chemicals
body:
One of the best soaps to use for both your body and hair wash. After trying all kinds of soaps over the years - every imaginable brand that you can think of, this one takes the top honours purely due to its less or negligible chemical usage.You won't find much lather in this soap - but that's a good thing. Most soap companies add chemicals to increase lather which makes you feel that you are getting a bang for your buck. But that's an eyewash. In the desire to get more lather, you can be exposing yourself to more chemicals.I have a very good friend who supplies chemicals to shampoo and soap manufacturers. His family does not use any branded shampoos and soaps. Even they use Medimix and Chandrika - cause he knows how bad the chemicals are in all these soaps and shampoos.Since I have started using Medimix (also use Chandrika many times) for washing my hair, I don't have any dandruff, I haven't lost any hair (am 50 yrs, proud to hit this milestone), and amongst most of my peers group of friends and colleagues - I am the very few who has not gone bald.(Pro Tip - I also use Coconut Oil mixed with Castor Oil almost every alternate day. Its a super combination to keep hair in good healthy condition).

body:
My vacuum Machine burned out as a result of an electrical problem. The company's help line received my complaint, and Mr. Jayanta Badal, a member of the service team, quickly and effectively addressed my concerns. He replaced parts for me, and his manner of speech and helpfulness had really pleased me. Mrs. Sanna occasionally conducts follow-up.I had never anticipated receiving this level of careI'm grateful to Mr. Jayanta and Mrs. Sanna.Product details.I recently purchased a vacuum cleaner and I am absolutely thrilled with its performance! This vacuum cleaner is hands down one of the best purchases I have ever made. It is incredibly efficient and easy to use.One of the standout features of this vacuum cleaner is its powerful suction. It can pick up even the tiniest particles from my carpet and hardwood floors with ease. The machine is also very lightweight, so I can carry it up and down the stairs without any difficulty.Another great thing about this vacuum cleaner is that it comes with a variety of attachments that make cleaning different surfaces and hard-to-reach areas a breeze. The crevice tool, for example, is perfect for getting into tight corners and under furniture, while the upholstery tool is great for cleaning furniture and drapes.The vacuum cleaner is also surprisingly quiet. I can clean my entire house without disturbing anyone, even my sleeping baby!Overall, I am extremely pleased with my purchase and would highly recommend this vacuum cleaner to anyone in the market for a new one. It is efficient, easy to use, and comes with a range of attachments that make cleaning a breeze.

title:

Quality was good
body:
Discovering the Wedani Women's Casual Floral Top was like stumbling upon a hidden gem in the world of fashion. As someone who values both style and comfort, I'm thrilled to share my experience with this delightful wardrobe addition.The first thing that caught my attention was the captivating floral print. The intricate details and vibrant colors of the flowers bring a touch of nature's beauty to the fabric. The print is tastefully done, neither too overwhelming nor too subtle, making it suitable for a range of occasions - from casual outings to relaxed gatherings with friends.What truly sets this top apart is its impeccable blend of casual and chic elements. The design effortlessly combines a relaxed fit with a subtle elegance, making it a versatile choice for various settings. The loose, flowing silhouette allows for unrestricted movement and provides a comfortable fit without compromising on style.The fabric's quality is noticeable from the moment you touch it. The top is crafted from a soft and breathable material that feels wonderful against the skin, making it perfect for all-day wear. Whether you're running errands or lounging around, you'll appreciate the comfort it offers.The attention to detail in the stitching and construction of the Wedani Women's Casual Floral Top is commendable. The seams are neatly finished, and the overall craftsmanship exudes a sense of durability. This is a top that's built to last beyond just a season.One aspect I truly adore about this top is its versatility. It pairs effortlessly with various bottoms - be it jeans, leggings, or even a skirt. The wide neckline and subtle flare at the hem add a touch of femininity that complements different body types.In terms of sizing, Wedani seems to have struck the right balance. The size chart provided is accurate, and the fit was exactly as expected. This attention to sizing details is a testament to the brand's commitment to customer satisfaction.Ordering the Wedani Women's Casual Floral Top was a breeze. The website was user-friendly, and the shipping was prompt. The top arrived neatly packaged, reflecting the brand's dedication to delivering a positive customer experience.In conclusion, the Wedani Women's Casual Floral Top has truly exceeded my expectations. Its blend of style, comfort, and quality make it a must-have for any fashion-conscious individual seeking a versatile wardrobe piece. From its captivating floral print to its relaxed yet chic design, this top is a true representation of modern casual elegance. I can confidently recommend the Wedani Women's Casual Floral Top to anyone looking to effortlessly elevate their everyday style.

product: Espoir Exclusive Day & Date Display Analog White Dial Stainless Steel Men's Watch - WDD0507, Medium
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Great Looks and Accurate Time Keeping!
body:
Though I am not a fan of 40+ mm dial size, I bought it for red coloured seconds hand. The white dial proved to be quite helpful in quickly reading the time even with very small amount of light. But the most surprising fact was good time keeping by this watch supported by Day as well as Date tracking. The stainless steel chain has double lock like Casio watch and it can be adjusted for any wrist size by simply sliding the lock position. Despite the size, this watch is light enough to remain comfortable on the wrist. So yes, do give it a try. You will not be disappointed.Update: The watch needed a change of battery after 13 months of operation. In these 13 months of use, I had to adjust time being kept by it just three or four times. That means, it keeps correct time for almost 3 months in a row!

product: Park Avenue Voyage Amazon Woods Perfume, 120ml
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
A Decent Choice: Park Avenue Voyage Amazon Woods Perfume Review
body:
The Park Avenue Voyage Amazon Woods Perfume offers a fair option for those seeking an affordable fragrance. While it might not be a standout in the world of perfumery, it has its merits that make it worth considering. Here's an overview of its performance:Scent Profile:The Amazon Woods fragrance by Park Avenue presents a blend of woody and fresh notes. The scent is subtle and balanced, with hints of woods and earthiness. It's not overly intense, making it suitable for everyday wear.Longevity:The longevity of the fragrance is average. It might last for a few hours after application but tends to fade relatively quickly compared to more premium perfumes. Reapplication might be necessary to maintain the scent throughout the day.Sillage (Projection):The sillage or projection of the perfume is moderate, which means it's noticeable but doesn't overwhelm your surroundings. This can be a plus for those who prefer a more subdued presence of fragrance.Versatility:The Amazon Woods fragrance is versatile and can be worn in various settings, whether it's a casual day out or a work environment. Its balanced and non-intrusive nature makes it suitable for a wide range of occasions.Packaging:The packaging of the perfume is simple and functional. It comes in a standard bottle with a spray mechanism for easy application. While not particularly luxurious, it's practical for everyday use.Affordable Option:One of the strong points of the Park Avenue Voyage Amazon Woods Perfume is its affordability. It provides a fragrance experience without the high price tag associated with designer or luxury perfumes.Average Uniqueness:While the scent profile is pleasant, it might lack the uniqueness and complexity that higher-end fragrances offer. It might not stand out as a signature scent but can still be appreciated for its simplicity.Average Quality:The quality of the fragrance is decent for its price point. It's important to note that it might not have the same depth and richness as more expensive perfumes, but it still offers a fair experience.Personal Preference:Fragrance preferences are highly subjective. What might be appealing to some might not resonate with others. It's recommended to test the fragrance on your skin before making a decision.In summary, the Park Avenue Voyage Amazon Woods Perfume provides a fair option for those seeking an affordable and versatile fragrance. While it might not offer the same level of complexity and longevity as higher-end perfumes, it still manages to provide a decent scent experience for daily use. If you're looking for an everyday fragrance that won't break the bank, the Amazon Woods perfume might be a reasonable choice.

product: MASQ By Q-One Blossom Reusable, Washable, Anti-Bacterial (BFE>99%) 4 Layer Embroidered, Fashionable Cotton Cloth Face Mask...
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Most comfortable face masks for women
body:
This mask is both beautiful and comfortable. I haven't worn a more comfortable one yet from the beginning of lockdown. I have a chubby face so most masks pull at my earlobes and make me want to pull them down constantly. I ordered these in large and they are so perfect for me. They cover my face without suffocating me and the handle is also quite soft and adjustable. I love going out now. Most of the time I don't even realise I am wearing a mask, it is that comfortable and breathable. They are also a little rigid so its great to keep them in shape without the need of those metal ones around nose that is always a pain and sometimes even blocks the radius of my vision. Clearly my most fav mask yet. Kudos.

product: Espoir Exclusive Day & Date Display Analog White Dial Stainless Steel Men's Watch - WDD0507, Medium
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Great Looks and Accurate Time Keeping!
body:
Though I am not a fan of 40+ mm dial size, I bought it for red coloured seconds hand. The white dial proved to be quite helpful in quickly reading the time even with very small amount of light. But the most surprising fact was good time keeping by this watch supported by Day as well as Date tracking. The stainless steel chain has double lock like Casio watch and it can be adjusted for any wrist size by simply sliding the lock position. Despite the size, this watch is light enough to remain comfortable on the wrist. So yes, do give it a try. You will not be disappointed.Update: The watch needed a change of battery after 13 months of operation. In these 13 months of use, I had to adjust time being kept by it just three or four times. That means, it keeps correct time for almost 3 months in a row!

body:
Yes one of the best suited for my purpose - I have black, blue and 1 card holder in blue as well, all from Daily ObjectsPros:1.  Perfect size 10/10! Really thin and perfect for card holder / lean wallet in real sense (5 bank cards, cash with 8 to 10 notes of varying sizes, 2 PP size pics, 3-4 coins, 1 plain key of door and 1-2 slips /bills - all fits in properly2. Nylon it is so washable and easy to clean, no worries of water / rains or sweating damage like in leather wallets. I did order one faux leather but returned as I did not like colour printed on it and single button for closing the flap. Lasting material! Using black one since 6 months almost3. Anyone with spine or disc issues are advised not to keep wallet in back pocket, so this one is a boon for them w/o bulge in front trouser pocket or shirt pocket for sure4. 2 brass button really makes it secure for things to not fall in wallet or outside** Can carry it in temples (many dont allow leather stuff inside Garbh).Cons:1. High price for sure even though they say ballistic nylon (- 1 star)2. Daily Object should pay attention to finishing more than packing and boxes, lose threads and glue was found in my first order of black wallet / card holder3. Delivery usually takes longer time than average for this seller - seen in all 3 ordersI liked Blue color more (nylon) than Black - fine for casual as well as formal for sure! product: Soulflower Tea Tree Hair Oil | Hair Growth, Scalp Nourishment, Anti Dandruff | Pure, Natural, & Cold Pressed | Tea Tree Es...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Thoroughly impressed! Highly recommended!!
body:
The media could not be loaded.
                



 Love love love this oil!The oil is thick in consistency so a bit difficult to apply but that’s probably because some of the oils like castor are actually thick. Anyhow I was impressed that they chose to give it thick, rather than dilute it and compromise on the quality. The oil seems to the original and genuine. You can mix it with some coconut oil for easy application.Second, the aroma! Oh the oil smells just so wonderful! The blend of so many aromatic oils makes you feel so good as the smell diffuses around when you leave it on your hair for a while. Particularly it’s the rosemary and lavender oil that stands out.The pricing maybe a bit on the higher side compared to routine hair oils but I guess you have to pay the price if you don’t want to compromise on the quality. Also considering the combination of oils used, it’s worth it.The packaging was good. It comes in a plastic spill proof bottle with a flip open and shut type of cap. There’s a plastic stopper under the cap which can be pierced to let the oil flow out.I can’t comment on the results as I have just started using it. But I have a strong feeling it would be positive, and I’m definitely sticking to this brand.The only suggestion I’d like to make is that the ingredients be listed on the product along with the ratio or quantity of each oil.I would highly recommend this hair oil!! Happy and satisfied customer !

product: WOW Skin Science Coconut Milk Shampoo For Hair Fall/Strength/Damage/Thinning - 300ml
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
JUST WOW !!!
body:
WOW Coconut Milk Shampoo is just amazing product. It is now one of my favorite shampoo. It has a eye catching pakaging. Also it's leak proof and has nice strong plastic pakaging. It has a pump out system to get the product out and also the pump is lockable which is amazing. No wastage of product will occur. The consistency of the shampoo is quite liquid runny and is pale yellow in colour. It easily spreads all over hair and easy to use too. The net quantity is 300ml and it retails for about 499Rs. It may get in cheaper price when sales goes on. WOW Apple Cider Vinegar shampoo includes natural ingredients such as apple cider, Vinegar, almond oil, argon oil etc which are definitely beneficial for healthy hairs. It is cruelty and vegan free. Best part about this shampoo is that it is also Paraben, alcohol, sulphate and mineral oil free. It sort outs the most often problems like dandruff. Slowly day be day application removes dandruff and cleans the scalp. It makes hairs Naturally smooth and shiny. Also makes hairs silky and manageable. I saw after two washes in a week, the dandruff gets invisible and it repairs split ends too. The fragrance of its is like fresh apple or we can say has a fruity smell which is mild and non irritable. If your hair is frizzy, dry, rough, use condition after this shampoo use. This shampoo can be used both my men and women. It is for all hair types. Try it once. You would love the product because I too liked it so I would definately recommend to you guys.

product: Casio G-Shock Digital Grey Dial Men's Watch-DW-5600E-1VQ (G001)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
EXCELLENT WATCH. BEAUTIFUL ELEGANT AND TOUGH.
body:
CASIO G-SHOCK DW-5600E-1VQ (G001)Writting this review more or less after 2 months of usage.Pros:1.Display- It is very clean and quickly readable at one glance at any any given situation.2.Features- 12 hour & 24 hour display, Date, Month, Day, 1 Alarm (Daily, Particular Day, Monthly, Yearly), Hourly Chime, Countdown Timer with Auto Repeat, Stopwatch with split second function and Flash Alert. Very basic but very useful. Although basic features makes the watch easy to use and less complicated.3.Backlight- Mild in perfect sense. Not too dim and not too strong. Display is perfectly visible in low light or no light situation.4.Button function- Buttons are a bit small and not easily accessible but in case of an accidental knock or fall no button gets activated on its own. So it serves a purpose. The 'Adjust' button is intentionally more covered than other three buttons so that in case of a knock it does not activates the time setting mode, it is not manufacturing defect.5.Fit and comfort- As the watch is light weight it is very comfortable of all day wear and it hugs my wrist very well. According to me those who have small wrist they can definitely wear this watch without felling any difficulty or discomfort. I wear this watch on the 5th hole (from dial side) so the end of the strap sticks out a bit but visually it does not looks bad to me, I like it.6.Accuracy- No deviation till now. Dead precise.Cons:NONE. Tried to find but NONE.Personal view- This watch looks very beautiful and elegant and tough at the same time, modern with touch of vintage. The most important thing is it does not looks like a smartwatch which I am very happy about, it has its own unique timelees style. Brand wise there is nothing to say as this is a CASIO and on top of that a G-SHOCK, so this is time tested and reliable. There are many many G-SHOCKS models but this model in particular is something else. Quality is up to the mark. Totally value for money, no disappointment worth every paisa. And a great thank you to the seller and delivery persons who sent and carried the watch and watch box at very good condition, not the watch was defective nor the watch box was damaged. TOTALLY SATISFIED.
Read more

product: Casio G-Shock Digital Grey Dial Men's Watch-DW-5600E-1VQ (G001)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Amazing and sturdy watch
body:
I read comments throughout shopping apps before purchasing it, and decided to rather rely on my own experience of the product. Till now it has been amazing. The strap was a bit small for my wrist but an extra long strap would sometimes be a hassle. Other than that, the side button on the top left is hard to press since it triggers the adjusting mechanism for the watch and hence it makes sense for it to be the hardest to press. Other buttons are pretty light and fun to use. The watch comes with warranty card, bill from amazon, and user manual. You can also find some videos on YouTube. The screen is also surrounded by an elevated protection so if you are wearing a kada or bracelet on the same hand, it does not scratch. The dial is a bit bigger than f91w and the arrangement of features makes the time easily readable. The LED light is very good on this. It illuminates the dial completely and evenly. So far so good. 10/10 would recommend

product: Casio G-Shock Digital Grey Dial Men's Watch-DW-5600E-1VQ (G001)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Solid watch. 10/10
body:
Quality of this watch is top notch as expected. Amazon did a great job in delivering the product, the package was well packed and got delivered within a short amount of time.Watch is super light weight and sturdy, fits well on my hand. As for the features it provides a stopwatch, a timer and an alarm clock where the alarm can be scheduled daily, monthly or according to a specific date. The alarm sound isn't that loud but isn't too low either. Overall it's a super comfortable minimalistic watch and can be used as a daily driver even in harsh situations.The adjust button will be a little recessed because that's how it's designed originally - to avoid changing the values by mistake. One might want to take off the watch to use that button but I'm not too bothered by it because it's a button I'll use rarely.Altogether this watch is a 10/10 for me and I'd like to recommend this to everyone who's interested in owning a good quality G-Shock which is well worth the price.

body:
I bought this product on experimental basis to stop a leaking GI sheet joint, after trying and failing duct tape and silicon. It is very easy to apply and I did not do a second or third coat, though the manual insists to do, since the joint is not easily accessible. But to my surprise, the leak stopped completely and even after heavy rains, still remain so. Encouraged by this, I applied two coats above the fire wall of my Mahindra Bolero, which was persistingly leaking water even after applying body filler, glue and even m-seal. That also working like a charm and the leak has stopped. I recommend this product to every one, as it is worth every penny paid.

product: TIMEWEAR Timewear Slim Series Analog Women's Watch (Multicolour Dial Colored Strap)
title:
1.0 out of 5 stars
Bad quality strip
body:
I purchased this watch 7 months ago and was initially impressed by its design and functionality. However, after just a few weeks of wearing it, I noticed that the strap was of poor quality and began to deteriorate rapidly. The material felt cheap and flimsy, and the buckle had already started to show signs of wear and tear.Unfortunately, after 1 month of purchase, the strap completely broke off the watch, rendering it completely unusable. I am very disappointed in the poor quality of this product and the fact that it lasted only one month before becoming unusable.I would not recommend this watch to anyone looking for a reliable and durable timepiece. While the design and functionality may be appealing, the poor quality of the strap makes this a poor choice for daily wear. Save your money and invest in a more durable and reliable watch.

product: Sujata Dynamix DX Mixer Grinder, 900W, 3 Jars (White,Plastic)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Screams quality!
body:
My very first purchase from the house of Sujata. I researched high and low for a new mixer grinder after my 27 years old Usha was given away (it still worked!) and my final two picks were Panasonic and Sujata. Both these brands are high on quality, durability and workmanship. I've read reviews of many people owning them for more than a decade; although Sujata mixers running continuously have the highest number i.e. of 30+ years!I wanted an upgrade on both quality and wattage from my previous single jar 750 watt Usha. Panasonic didn't have a very high wattage with their highest model fixed on 750 watts; the Monster model which I found quite nice. I read quite a few reviews of people complaining of the lid locking system not sitting right, because of which the grinder wouldn't run. This was a kicker. Buying their lid alone isn't very cheap, plus any locking mechanism failure will render the whole unit unusable. I was willing to overlook this, but the repairing costs after the warranty period was the deal-breaker for me. The parts are not readily available and the repairing isn't easy and cheap. I was obviously looking for a long time gig in the mixer purchase, so I wasn't too happy on these parameters. Another not-so-important reason was the option of adding a third-party food processor attachment. No such attachments are currently available in the market for Panasonic, which was a bummer!Sujata scored on quality, robustness, longevity, parts availability and third-party attachment options. I purchased the Dynamix for Rs.5790 and supplemented it with the robust aluminium-base Frootmix blender jar from Flipkart for Rs.915, together costing me Rs. 6705 which worked out to be a great deal. I had first ordered the Supermix model and ordered the large 1500ml steel jar separately, but upon more research, I found out that the middle 1 litre jar of both the Dynamix and Supermix models are not the same, contrary to my assumption. One reviewer on YT found the Dynamix jar weighed heavier (by 30grams), had a wider lip, wider lid brim, thicker rubber gasket and flow breakers on the body, which are all absent on the Supermix jar. I found this out just in time and could cancel the order in transit and promptly ordered the Dynamix along with the Frootmix blender jug.The product quality is sublime. You can easily see the commitment  to quality by Sujata. The sincerity and abundance with which they make their original parts available (of the entire motor and all attachments) online and offline reminds me of the good old Maruti 800 car. Any problem with it and the nearest mechanic would easily find the right part at a great cost and repair it in a jiffy! I'm glad companies like Sujata are maintaining their quality and robustness for the last 45 years (Usha grinders were great in the 80s, and early 90s, but since the 2000s, their mixers are not as robust and long lasting as before).I first ground a 2kg mixture of dry fruits, which also consisted of fox nuts and 250gm of rock hard babool gum (or gond). I was done in less than 12 minutes! I was a little apprehensive about the gum as I usually fry it in ghee and then grind it, which makes it softer and fluffier and easier to grind. But this time I decided to test the grinder with the rock-hard pieces as is. I divided the quantity in 2 smaller portions and replaced the dome lid with a small steel lid as the gum pieces will initially be cut up and flung with a lot of force, potentially causing cracks or deep scratches on the original lid, and I wasn't taking a chance with this new baby. I pulsed the machine for a few seconds, then ran it on the lowest speed, stopping every few seconds. There was a noisy racket inside the jar! But after a few seconds, the hard gond turned into a fine shiny powder and there was no spillage on the lip whatsoever. What a success! I then used the small chutney jar to make a simple chutney and it was a delightful experience. The chutney was smooth and silky and although I didn't lock the lid with the clips provided and only held the lid down firmly, nothing spilled out on the outer rim.The motor sound is bearable and cannot be categorised as loud. It sounds smooth and supple. The wire is long and every part is thoughtfully made. The latest black option is also available which is priced around nearly 1000rs higher than the normal white model, but Sujata hasn’t released any separate black coloured attachment or part for this model which can lead to a colour mismatch if an additional jar/jug/lid is purchased later on.All in all, my Sujata experience has been great and I'll come back and update my adventures with it. I would wholeheartedly recommend this brand to anyone looking to buy a mixer/grinder.

product: Studds Chrome Eco Full Face Helmet- Black (L)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Good Product
body:
I am highly impressed with the Studds bike helmet I recently purchased. The helmet not only looks stylish but also provides exceptional comfort and safety features. The build quality is top-notch, offering a reassuringly sturdy feel without compromising on weight or ventilation. Ordering through Studds' platform was seamless, and the helmet arrived promptly, well-packaged to ensure it arrived in perfect condition. Overall, I'm extremely satisfied with my Studds helmet and would recommend it to anyone looking for a combination of style, comfort, and safety in a bike helmet.
Read more

product: Studds Chrome Eco Full Face Helmet- Black (L)
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Economy Helmet, Complete with all necessary features | Review | "Best in its price range"
body:
This time I was in search for a helmet with close design and casual looks. Again had only 2-3 brands in mind with Studds on top.So didn't wander around much and searched for Studds design. Going through many models, this one caught my attention and was finalized in one go owing to simplicity and cost to benefit ratio.Helmet along with safety accessory, is also a style statement. This one falls short of style statement but serves other purpose well. With solid build and good quality overall it’s a perfect company for your bike rides in lowest possible cost without compromising much on quality.▶ Using it past 8 months without any major issue.•••••••••••••••INSIDE BOX•••••••••••••••1. Helmet & Visor2. Guarantee card / ManualWeight: ~1kgFor size: Simply follow size chart in listing••••••••••••••FEATURES••••••••••••••1. Clear visor (available visor spare for purchase: smoke tint, mirror, and rainbow)2. Unpainted textured outer shell for extra scratch resistance3. Silicon hard coated visor.4. Quick release chain strap mechanism for easy operation5. Dynamic ventilation system, with air inlet on both sides.•••••••PROS•••••••1. Solid & sturdy design.2. Light weight & comfortable to wear.3. Winter benefit owing to close design. Less air enters helmet as opposed to open ones.4. Side vents are there on both sides for air passage to inner area which controls sweating to some extent.5. Textured finish on outer surface ensures extra scratch resistance and maintains looks for longer duration, as compared to painted one.6. Projected part on visor to help pull it up or down, without having fingerprints all over it.7. Quick release chain strap mechanism for fast & easy removal.8. Proper wind noise isolation at all speeds.9. Can be easily locked to vehicle using helmet locks, which is not the case with open helmets.10. Perfect fit as per size guide. Initially it will be a bit tight and adjust with time.•••••••CONS•••••••1. Close design results in less air flow inside leading to sweating and suffocation.2. For same reason, fogging occurs on visor during winters and its annoying.3. It also does not resonate well with spectacles and goggles.••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••VISOR- Scratch proof or not••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••Silicon hard coated visor, as mentioned by company is supposed to be scratch resistant.BUT remember its plastic in the end, and when scratches don’t even spare glass, then how far plastic can go. It’s prone to medium to heavy intensity scratches, but mild ones are slightly covered.Any helmet you purchase, cheaper or costlier, in few months or a year, visor becomes close to useless due to scratches and needs to be replaced for clear visibility. Unless you keep your helmet in safe and dont use it at all.•••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••OUTER SURFACE- Scratch proof or not•••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••Textured surface without paint is an add-on as it tends to avoid scratches, compared to painted glossy or matte surface. Even if there’s a scratch on surface, it becomes a part of the plastic, and is not an eyesore as compared to scratches on glossy surface.••••••••••••••••••••FINAL VERDICT••••••••••••••••••••▶ This helmet by Studds is casual looking durable product. It excels in many areas, tough yet comfortable, durable yet cheaper just that looks wise it’s a bit on lower side. So if looks don’t matter much and you are looking for light & durable helmet, you can go for it.▶ For more, sky is the limit. Be it looks, features, better quality etc. For few extra hundreds, Studds marshal is a good choice with premium looks and build quality, but with a bit of extra weight. Other variants ninja, motocross, downtown etc.▶ Then there're other brands too like Steelbird, Vega which come next and you may look out for those.▶ It’s all incomplete without reference to the internationals brand like HJC, LS2, AGV etc, which are worth considering for the quality they offer but then cost is on higher side and maximum people won’t spend so much on helmets. But for the ones who can, definitely give them a shot.

title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Good Quality Product
body:
Most of those lifting heavy weights in my gym use this wrist support. It is very sturdy and holds the wrist very well. Apart from using this for lifting weights, I used it for push ups, mountain climber and other exercises where I had previously felt pain in my wrists; it works very well. I felt very comfortable doing those exercises knowing that I've secured my wrists.Only thing is that since it goes around the wrist, while doing push ups etc, it tends to push into the upper part of the wrist (right below the palm) and is sometimes uncomfortable; but, that can be resolved by pushing it just a few inches below.

product: Kobo WTA-04 Power Cotton Gym Support with Thumb Support Grip Gloves (Black)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
|| Quality Wraps at a Very Low Cost ||
body:
For a full Unboxing & Hands On Review, watch my video on YouTube.|| Hands On Review ||Finally a quality wrist wraps which is surprisingly good (Coming from an Indian Made Brand) which does not burns whole in your pocket (Like other International Brands).This wraps comes in a pair, the length of each wraps is 20 inches (with Velcro).This is an elasticated wrist wrap with a good Velcro at the end to lock it in place and a loop to insert your thumb. The Stitching is strong and the material is also of good quality (especially at this price range).|| Usage Review ||At first getting the wraps correctly on is a hard task, but, with a few trail and error you will come at a sweet spot.Now as for usage review, i like to wear it on very heavy press movements with full ROM so getting the ROM was not a concern for me.So the tension of the wraps are doing fine and keeping my wrist in place and the grip stable and helped me on the way up. It keeps my joint tight, and after the session, my wrists are feeling fine.This is a must for people who are doing power-lifting & Strongman.Will update again, after prolong use.

product: Kobo WTA-04 Power Cotton Gym Support with Thumb Support Grip Gloves (Black)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
THE WRIST PROTECTOR!
body:
I have been using them for months now and gotta say that it was a great deal!Let's talk about pros and cons...Pros:-1) very effective for heavy pressing/pushing movement..because thats where you need more support...2) the thumb loop prevents it from moving from its place...3) helps a lot with CALISTHENICS! Some movement liek pike push ups....decline push ups or planche puts a lot of pressure on wrists....these do support the wrist and in my case they also reduced the wrist pain while doing those exercises...Cons:-1) it may become a little uncomfortable if you wear them tight for a longer period(which you dont have to)...loosen them between sets to allow the blood to flow2) the shape of the straps may change cuz of regular use ....it also depends upon how you wear them (how close to the palms do you wrap them) but this is pretty normal and isn't really an issue...Conclusion....just go for them without any doubt...defo. value for money...

product: Treo by Milton Store Fresh Square Glass Storage Container Set, 300ml, Set of 2, Transparent
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Very good containers
body:
Very good quality containers. Glass and lid quality- both extremely good. Decent capacity. I have seen containers with more capacity (370ml and 400ml) having less space as compared to these 300ml containers.Bought them for packing dry veggies for lunch box. Have a 350ml round Glasslock container for packing curries. These Treo 300ml ones, bought for packing dry vegetable alongside.But they are slightly big for that purpose. Was searching for 250ml/270ml containers- couldn't find any. Just found one option- Pasabahce snow box 270ml containers. But didn't go for them as the lids weren't clip open.Still these are just a notch bigger. Just a little more vegetable gets packed alongside the curry in the other box. That's it. Rest taking dry vegetable in Treo for lunch everyday. Suiting just fine.Though I received yellow rimmed lids as opposed to the white ones displayed here, which I wanted.Conclusion: Recommend it totally. Worth the amount paid.Update: The containers have a branding of Blinkmax on the glass and not Treo. Don't know if Blinkmax is Treo's brand only or not.Or if given a different company's product in Treo packaging. As they came packed in Treo branded box displaying these containers.Not sure! No issues with the quality though.

product: Amazon Brand - Solimo Non-Stick Tawa with 2-Way Non-Stick Coating, 26cm (Induction and Gas Stove Compatible), Aluminium, B...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Worked as expected for 10 months
body:
Dec-2022: It stopped working after 10 months. The string broke twice within this 10 months and i replaced it twice as well with the help of youtube videos... So dont expect too much... But during its working state, it was a great product.Feb-2022: Initially I rated it with 1 star and added the below comment (in quotes).Now, I would like to give it 5 stars. Because, as I doubted earlier, the way it was used was wrong. After a month long testing, I found that we should fill items till just above the topmost blade. Only then it will work as expected. Dont fill the tumbler full. Max fill only 75% or just above the topmost blade.With this approach, I am now successfully chopping Coconut, garlic, almost all vegetables.Also, the very first pull of the string should be done with bit force, for the blades to rotate between the items. Then automatically the subsequent pulls will be easier.So far so good with the product.#### Old Review - "I tried to chop ginger and garlic. Sadly nothing happened to it. So, i tried with garlic alone. Still no luck.Either i am doing something wrong, or this product is not designed for these. Attached is the video of what I did.Hope someone will respond on what to do."

product: The Bling Stores Unisex-adult Personalized Genuine Leather Passport Cover, Name Crafted (2 Charms, Black)
title:
1.0 out of 5 stars
Disappointing Passport Cover Experience
body:
I recently purchased a passport cover with high hopes of enhancing my travel experience, but unfortunately, it fell far short of my expectations.Firstly, let's discuss the name plate. The name plate on this passport cover was a major letdown. It was incredibly small and poorly designed, making it practically useless for identification purposes. Not only was the font choice unappealing, but the size made it difficult to read, defeating the purpose of having a name plate altogether. It felt like an afterthought rather than a functional feature.Moreover, the material used for this passport cover was nothing short of disappointing. It felt flimsy and cheap, which made me question its durability. I expected a sturdy and long-lasting cover, but instead, it seemed like it would easily tear or wear out over time. Additionally, the rigidity of the material made it frustrating to insert and remove the passport. It lacked the flexibility necessary for smooth and effortless handling, causing unnecessary hassle during airport security checks.Furthermore, the material choice was puzzling. It seemed susceptible to stains and fading, which is far from ideal for a travel accessory that is exposed to various conditions. Within a short period, the cover showed signs of wear and tear, which is unacceptable for an item meant to protect something as important as a passport.Overall, I regret my purchase of this passport cover. The name plate's poor design and small size, coupled with the cheap and flimsy material, left me thoroughly disappointed. I would not recommend this particular passport cover to anyone seeking a reliable and visually appealing travel accessory. Save your money and invest in a better-quality option that will provide the protection and durability you deserve for your passport.

product: SHOESHINE Shoe Trees (6 Pairs) Shoe Shapers Stretcher Adjustable Shoe Trees
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Good Product, But Needs an bigger mid-section
body:
Bought this for 664 (3-piece), which is slightly expensivePros:- Adjustability is a great feature, due to which you can share it with your family (Smallest size is around Indian 8 or 9 number shoe, Biggest is 11 number shoe)- Decent durable build, the material is good also, Lightweight as well.- Good 'Universal' shape, that didn't give me any issue in different shoes that I put this into.Cons:- Price could be lower, not ideal at the moment.- Biggest Con is that it doesn't support the mid-section of the shoe (see my shoe sized 10 in photo). I think the plastic part needs to be longer, so it doesn't just support the front section, without sacrificing adjustability.Workaround Tip:- Earlier I was only using old newspaper (crushed form) inside my shoes. Now I'm using this for my formal shoes (only) where this maintains the front section, and back heel properly, but in between I also add crushed newspaper to support the middle section of the shoes.

title:

body:
This Shoeshine Shoetree is a product that solves your 80 % problem at the cost of 20%.Pros:• It is cheap. You don't need to spend an arm and a leg for this.• It can be used for smallest to largest set of shoes considering it has multiple length settings.• It stretches your shoe hence prevents creases and wrinkles.Cons:• Since it is not made-up of high absorbing wood such as Cidar wood, it won't remove moisture from your shoe.(Advice: Don't use single shoe for extended periods of time on daily basis. The sweat/moisture will reduce the life of your leather-shoe.)• It looks and feels cheap as it is mainly made of plastic. (Not a complaint as it is indeed a cheap/introductory product in this category).My verdict:Scenario one: If you are on a tight budget and have leather-shoes then you can invest in this product.Case scenario two: If you own multiple shoes then you can buy this in bulk considering that this will be far cheaper than spending money on buying premium wood shoetree.This product is not for the sneakerheads.

product: Wipro Garnet A60 Base B22D 20-Watt LED Bulb (White, Pack of 1)
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Okay product, but great customer service from seller
body:
This bulb has excellent build quality and is heavier and larger and better made than normal Philips LED bulbs. Feels solid and not flimsy or cheaply made.However the bulb stopped working in around 7-8 months. I didn't know how to claim warranty and then the lockdown also happened in March, and I just left it. Towards the middle of June, just 15 days before the end of my warranty period I wrote to the seller (A..S) asking about how I could claim warranty. I was honestly not expecting any reply, but to my surprise I got an immediate reply asking me to ship the defective bulb back to their warehouse. I wrote back saying warranty was nearly over and that I hadn't asked earlier because of the lockdown but A..S said they would honour the warranty even if the item reached after June 30, when warranty would expire.I sent the bulb back, and as promised I received a replacement bulb, as well as tracking details. The product is decent, but you can be more assured because the seller is extremely professional, very quick to respond to queries and takes full responsibility for customer service. Highly recommend!
Read more

product: Neostreak Men's Slim Fit Stretchable Jeans
title:
1.0 out of 5 stars
Disappointing Quality - Neostreak Men's Jeans Review
body:
I recently purchased a pair of Neostreak Men's Jeans, and I have to say, it was a frustrating experience from the start. These jeans, unfortunately, failed to meet even the most basic expectations, and here's why I'm extremely dissatisfied:Zip Spoiled in 2 Months: One of the most glaring issues with these jeans is the quality of the zipper. It's mind-boggling how a pair of jeans could have a zipper malfunction within just two months of use. This not only led to embarrassing situations but also added an extra expense for repair.Questionable Durability: The very purpose of jeans is durability, but the Neostreak jeans I purchased don't seem to understand that. The fabric feels flimsy and wore out far too quickly. After only a few washes, I noticed signs of fading and thinning.Inconsistent Sizing: Sizing is a crucial aspect of buying jeans, and Neostreak's sizing chart seems to be misleading. The fit was far from what was indicated, making the jeans uncomfortable to wear.Lack of Comfort: Comfort is non-negotiable when it comes to jeans, but these failed to deliver. The material is rough and stiff, and the overall design lacks the flexibility that should come standard in a pair of jeans.Limited Style Choices: Neostreak's style offerings are quite limited, and this particular pair lacked the trendy or fashionable aspects that I look for in jeans. They feel outdated and uninspired.

title:

: Highly Effective Cockroach Killer Spray with Instant Results and Pleasant Fragrance!
body:
I recently purchased the HIT Crawling Insect Killer - Cockroach Killer Spray, and I must say it has completely exceeded my expectations. This review aims to highlight the key features that make this product exceptional: its effectiveness, instant action, deep-reach nozzle, and refreshing fragrance.First and foremost, the effectiveness of this cockroach killer spray is truly remarkable. Within moments of spraying, it delivers instant results by effectively eliminating crawling insects, especially cockroaches. I was amazed at how quickly it acted, providing immediate relief from the presence of these unwanted pests. This product certainly lives up to its promise of delivering swift action against insects.The deep-reach nozzle of the spray is a standout feature. It allows me to reach those hard-to-access areas where cockroaches often hide, such as cracks, crevices, and corners. The spray disperses evenly and accurately, ensuring that the product reaches the target areas effectively. This feature greatly enhances the product's overall efficiency in eradicating crawling insects from my home.One aspect I particularly appreciate about this cockroach killer spray is its fresh fragrance. Unlike many other insecticides that have a strong, unpleasant odor, this product emits a pleasant scent that helps mask any lingering insect-related odors. It leaves behind a refreshing aroma that adds a touch of cleanliness to the treated areas. This is especially important for me as I prefer to have a clean and inviting environment in my home.The spray's long-lasting effects are worth mentioning as well. Even after application, it continues to provide protection against crawling insects for an extended period. This means that I can enjoy a pest-free environment without the need for constant reapplication. It's reassuring to know that this product offers long-lasting efficacy, ensuring peace of mind for a significant duration.Another notable advantage of this product is its user-friendly design. The spray bottle is easy to handle, with a comfortable grip that allows for precise application. The instructions provided are clear and concise, making it simple to use even for those who are not accustomed to handling insecticides. The packaging is sturdy and leak-proof, ensuring that the product remains intact and ready to use whenever needed.In summary, the HIT Crawling Insect Killer - Cockroach Killer Spray is an exceptional product that delivers on its promises. With its impressive effectiveness, instant action, deep-reach nozzle, and pleasant fragrance, it has become my go-to solution for eliminating crawling insects, particularly cockroaches, from my home. I highly recommend this product to anyone in need of a reliable and efficient insecticide.Pros:- Highly effective in eliminating crawling insects, especially cockroaches- Provides instant results for immediate relief- Deep-reach nozzle for targeting hard-to-access areas- Pleasant fragrance that masks unpleasant odors- Long-lasting effects for extended protection- User-friendly design with clear instructionsOverall, this cockroach killer spray deserves a five-star rating for its exceptional performance and ease of use. It has become an indispensable tool in my battle against crawling insects, and I'm confident it will meet the needs of anyone seeking a reliable and effective solution.

title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Perfect Blend of Style and Functionality!
body:
I recently purchased the DEIN KLEIDER Polyester Sling Cross Body Shoulder Bag, and I couldn't be happier with my choice. This bag has exceeded my expectations in every way possible.First and foremost, the design is sleek and modern, making it suitable for both men and women. The high-quality polyester material looks great and feels durable and well-crafted. I appreciate the attention to detail in the stitching and overall construction, which gives it a premium feel.The size of the bag is just right for my needs. It comfortably fits all my daily essentials, including my laptop, notebook, charger, and water bottle. The multiple compartments and pockets are incredibly handy for keeping things organized, which is a big plus for someone like me, who is always on the go.The crossbody design is not only stylish but also incredibly functional. It distributes the weight evenly across my shoulder, making it comfortable to wear for extended periods. The adjustable strap allows for customization to fit my body perfectly.What truly sets this bag apart is its versatility. Whether heading to the office, travelling, or simply going about my day, this bag adapts effortlessly. It's become my go-to choice for business meetings, airport travel, and casual outings with friends.Overall, the DEIN KLEIDER Polyester Sling Cross Body Shoulder Bag is an exceptional product that combines style, functionality, and durability. If you're looking for a versatile bag that can handle your busy lifestyle while keeping you organized and looking great, I highly recommend trying this one. It's a five-star product through and through!

title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
An Amazing Piece of Mechanical Watch
body:
I am a proud owner of this watch, this is an amazing piece of mechanical watch, if u want to own a chronographic watch and u have the budget consider this watch.The black coloured watch is a delight to see. It is of high quality and heavier than a average metal watch but as you know it's meant for a strong person having strong wrist.I had visited a Authorised Casio store in Pune Camp to Adjust the length of the belt, the customer service was quick and up to mark. I was not charged for the service.Update : After using this watch for more than 18 months i'm totally impressed by its quality and toughness. Even though it looks delicate, this is a very Strong and Durable watch. i have continuously weared it for office, biking and while travelling. it is scratch resistant and water proof. there is no water vapour on the dail of the watch even after getting drenched in rain.

The premature removal of the rose gold plating not only affects the aesthetic appeal of the earrings but also raises concerns about the overall quality and craftsmanship.I had high hopes for these earrings, considering their initial appearance, but the quick deterioration has left me regretting my purchase. I believe it's essential to share my experience with others to prevent them from facing a similar disappointment.In summary, I strongly advise potential buyers to reconsider purchasing these earrings and explore alternative options that offer better quality and longevity.

product: Havells Efficiencia Neo 1200mm BLDC Motor with remote Ceiling Fan (Elegant White), 26 Watt, Winner of “National Energy Con...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Less Bill. With Style
body:
I was looking for a new ceiling fan for my living room, and I came across this Havells Efficiencia Neo 1200mm BLDC Motor with remote Ceiling Fan . I was impressed by the features and the ratings, so I decided to give it a try. I ordered it from Amazon and it arrived in just two days, well packed and protected. The installation was easy and quick, thanks to the clear instructions and the helpful customer support.The fan looks amazing in my living room, with its modern design and aesthetic brown color. It matches well with my furniture and decor. The remote control is very convenient and easy to use. I can adjust the speed and the timer settings with just a click of a button. The fan is very quiet and smooth, even at high speeds. It circulates the air efficiently and cools the room quickly. The best part is that it consumes very little power, only 26 watts, which saves me a lot of money on electricity bills. It is also eco-friendly and has won the National “Energy Conservation Award 2021” for its performance.I am very happy with this purchase and I would highly recommend this fan to anyone who is looking for a reliable, stylish and energy-efficient ceiling fan. It is worth every penny and more. Havells has done a great job with this product and I hope they continue to make such quality products in the future.
